reviews.review_text:
good days gone by............ two nights at the ole' brendan byrne, wow it seems so long ago we were all hangin' and enjoying the spring tours. I always thought the dead played great here and this was no exception Space-terrapin-the other one stood out for me on that particular voyage. the 1st set dancin' was real sweet too.gettin down with the joker, the doran bros. and mr schick. Brothers of days gone by great trips.......... 
p.s. Surachi tapes are gooood.........

Epic JACK STRAW The title says it all. One of my all time favorites, and one of THEE most rocking kick ass Jack Straws to exist. This AUD recording is amazing, i love a good mix of AUD and SBD sound, this seems to have that, love to get the reactions from the fans in there w/o sacrificing overall sound. Phil drops bombs, Jerry tears it hard. A must listen! The feel like a stranger is also quite nice IMO. Havent listened to much else of the show, just remembered this J straw and forgot how amazing it really is. Anything with a Gem in it like this deserves a 5 star rating.
